{"id":319203,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/译言-中国大熊猫租借业务是如何运作的/","date":"2013-10-22T07:53:18Z","modified":"2016-01-06T06:53:03Z","title":"译言 | 中国大熊猫租借业务是如何运作的","content":"<p><strong>租借大熊猫可是个大买卖，不过，拥有大熊猫的花费也是非常昂贵的。中国保留着全世界大熊猫的所有权，中国会将大熊猫有选择性的借给他国，一对大熊猫租借一年的费用通常是100万美元，所得资金会用于中国的大熊猫保护工作。一般租期为10年，到期可选择续租。</strong></p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-319203 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/%e8%af%91%e8%a8%80-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e5%a4%a7%e7%86%8a%e7%8c%ab%e7%a7%9f%e5%80%9f%e4%b8%9a%e5%8a%a1%e6%98%af%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e8%bf%90%e4%bd%9c%e7%9a%84/22140328_47759/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/10/22140328_47759-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/10/22140328_47759-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/10/22140328_47759-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/%e8%af%91%e8%a8%80-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e5%a4%a7%e7%86%8a%e7%8c%ab%e7%a7%9f%e5%80%9f%e4%b8%9a%e5%8a%a1%e6%98%af%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e8%bf%90%e4%bd%9c%e7%9a%84/22140615_28178/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/10